title: Playoff Talk with Serena Winters
itunes:title: Playoff Talk with Serena Winters
description:
Miles and Jack were joined by Bally Sports Cleveland's Serena Winters on the latest episode of Mad Boosties. The trio continued breaking down the playoff action and discussed some of Serena's experiences covering the Kobe/Pau Lakers, the Blazers, Sixers and Cavs throughout the years.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
